quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  20,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  20,1,Taa-Haa
  20,2,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum par quran is liye nazil nahikiya ke tum mushaqqat mein par jao
  20,3,balkay is shakhs ko nasiyaat dainay ke liye ( nazilkiya hai ) jo khauf rakhta hai
  20,4,yeh is ( zaat bartar ) ka utaara howa hai jis ne zameen aur ounchay ounchay aasman banaye
  20,5,( yani khuday-e ) rehman jis ne arsh par qarar pakra
  20,6,jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai aur jo kuch un dono ke beech mein hai aur jo kuch ( zameen ki ) matti ke neechay hai sab isi ka hai
  20,7,aur agar tum pukaar kar baat kaho to woh to chupay bhaid aur nihayat posheeda baat taq ko jaanta hai
  20,8,( woh mabood brhq hai ke ) is ke siwa koi mabood nahi hai. is ke ( sab ) naam achay hain
  20,9,aurkiya tumhe moose ( ke haal ) ki khabar mili hai
  20,10,jab unhon ne aag dekhi to apne ghar walon se kaha ke tum ( yahan ) thehro mein ne aag dekhi hai ( mein wahan jata hon ) shayad is mein se mein tumahray paas angraai lau ya aag ( ke maqam ) ka rasta maloom karsakeoon
  20,11,jab wahan puhanche to aawaz aayi ke moose
  20,12,mein to tumhara perwar-digaar hon to apni jotiyan utaar do. tum ( yahan ) pak maidan ( yani ) tawee mein ho
  20,13,aur mein ne tum ko intikhab karliya hai to jo hukum diya jaye usay suno
  20,14,be shak mein hi khuda hon. mere siwa koi mabood nahi to meri ibadat karo aur meri yaad ke liye namaz parha karo
  20,15,qayamat yaqeenan anay wali hai. mein chahta hon ke is ( ke waqt ) ko posheeda rakhon taakay har shakhs jo koshish kere is ka badla paye
  20,16,to jo shakhs is par imaan nahi rakhta aur apni khwahish ke peechay chalta hai ( kahin ) tum ko is ( ke yaqeen ) se rok nah day to ( is soorat mein ) tum halaak hojao
  20,17,aur moose yeh tumahray dahinay haath meinkiya hai
  20,18,unhon ne kaha yeh meri laathi hai. is par mein sahara lagaata hon aur is se apni bakrion ke liye pattay jharta hon aur is mein mere liye aur bhi kayi faiday hain
  20,19,farmaya ke moose usay daal do
  20,20,to unhon ne is ko daal diya aur woh nagahan saanp ban kar dornay laga
  20,21,khuda ne farmaya ke usay pakar lau aur darna mat. hum is ko abhi is ki pehli haalat par lota den ge
  20,22,aur apna haath apni baghal se lagalo woh kisi aib ( o bemari ) ke baghair safaid ( chamakta dmkta ) niklay ga. ( yeh ) doosri nishani ( hai )
  20,23,taakay hum tumhe apne nishanaat azeem deikhein
  20,24,tum firaon ke paas jao ( ke ) woh sarkash ho raha hai
  20,25,kaha mere perwar-digaar ( is kaam ke liye ) mera seenah khol day
  20,26,aur mera kaam aasaan kardey
  20,27,aur meri zabaan ki girah khol day
  20,28,taakay woh baat samajh len
  20,29,aur mere ghar walon mein se ( aik ko ) mera wazeer ( yani madadgaar ) muqarrar farma
  20,30,( yani ) mere bhai Haroon ko
  20,31,is se meri qowat ko mazboot farma
  20,32,aur usay mere kaam mein shareek kar
  20,33,taakay hum teri bohat si tasbeeh karen
  20,34,aur tujhe kasrat se yaad karen
  20,35,to hum ko ( har haal mein ) dekh raha hai
  20,36,farmaya moose tumhari dua qubool ki gayi
  20,37,aur hum ne tum par aik baar aur bhi ahsaankiya tha
  20,38,jab hum ne tumhari walida ko ilhamkiya tha jo tumhe bataya jata hai
  20,39,( woh yeh tha ) ke usay ( yani moose ko ) sandooq mein rakho phir is ( sandooq ) ko darya mein daal do to darya usay kinare par daal day ga ( aur ) mera aur is ka dushman usay utha le ga. aur ( moose ) mein ne tum par apni taraf se mohabbat daal di hai ( is liye ke tum par meharbani ki jaye ) aur is liye ke tum mere samnay parwarish pao
  20,40,jab tumhari behan ( firaon ke haan ) gayi aur kehnay lagi ke mein tumhe aisa shakhs batau jo is ko paley. to ( is tareeq se ) hum ne tum ko tumhari maa ke paas pouncha diya taakay un ki ankhen thandhi hon aur woh ranj nah karen. aur tum ne 1 shakhs ko maar dala to hum ne tum ko gham se mukhlasi di aur hum ne tumhari ( kayi baar ) azmaish ki. phir tum kayi saal ahal Mudin mein thehray rahay. phir ae moose tum ( qabliyat risalat ke ) andazay par aa puhanche
  20,41,aur mein ne tum ko apne ( kaam ke ) liye banaya hai
  20,42,to tum aur tumhara bhai dono hamari nishanain le kar jao aur meri yaad mein susti nah karna
  20,43,dono firaon ke paas jao woh sarkash ho raha hai
  20,44,aur is se narmi se baat karna shayad woh ghhor kere ya dar jaye
  20,45,dono kehnay lagey ke hamaray perwar-digaar hamein khauf hai ke hum par ta-adi karne lagey ya ziyada sarkash hojaye
  20,46,khuda ne farmaya ke daro mat mein tumahray sath hon ( aur ) santa aur daikhta hon
  20,47,( acha ) to is ke paas jao aur kaho ke hum aap ke perwar-digaar ke beje hue hain to bani Israel ko hamaray sath jaane ki ijazat dijiye. aur inhen azaab nah kijiye. hum aap ke paas aap ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se nishani le kar aeye hain. aur jo hadaayat ki baat manay is ko salamti ho
  20,48,hamari taraf yeh wahi aayi hai ke jo jhutla-ay aur munhh phairay is ke liye azaab ( tayyar ) hai
  20,49,( gharz moose aur Haroon firaon ke paas gay ) is ne kaha ke moose tumhara perwar-digaar kon hai ?
  20,50,kaha ke hamara perwar-digaar woh hai jis ne har cheez ko is ki shakal vsort bakhsh phir raah dikhayi
  20,51,kaha to pehli jamaaton kakiya haal ?
  20,52,kaha ke un ka ilm mere perwar-digaar ko hai ( jo ) kitaab mein ( likha howa hai ). mera perwar-digaar nah chokta hai nah bhulta hai
  20,53,woh ( wohi to hai ) jis ne tum logon ke liye zameen ko farsh banaya aur is mein tumahray liye raste jari kiye aur aasman se pani barsaya. phir is se anwaa o iqsaam ki mukhtalif roideedgiyan peda kee
  20,54,ke ( khud bhi ) khao aur apne charpayon ko bhi churao. be shak un ( baton ) mein aqal walon ke liye ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
  20,55,isi ( zameen ) se hum tum ko pedakiya aur isi mein tumhe lota-ayn ge aur isi se doosri dafaa nikalen ge
  20,56,aur hum ne firaon ko apni sab nishanain deikhein magar woh takzib o ankaar hi karta raha
  20,57,kehnay laga ke moose tum hamaray paas is liye aeye ho ke apne jaadoo ( ke zor ) se hamein hamaray malik se nikaal do
  20,58,to hum bhi tumahray maqabil aisa hi jaadoo layein ge to hamaray aur apne darmain aik waqt muqarrar kar lau ke nah to hum is ke khilaaf karen aur nah tum ( aur yeh muqaabla ) aik hamwar maidan mein ( hoga )
  20,59,moose ne kaha aap ke liye ( muqablay ka ) din no roz ( muqarrarkiya jata hai ) aur yeh ke log is din chaasht ke waqt ikhatay ho jaien
  20,60,to firaon lout gaya aur apne samaan jama karkay phir aaya
  20,61,moose ne un ( gado garon) se kaha ke haae tumhari kambakhti. khuda par jhoot iftira nah karo ke woh tumhe azaab se fanaa kardey ga aur jis ne iftirakiya woh namuraad raha
  20,62,to woh baahum apne muamlay mein jhgrhane aur chupkay chupkay sargoshi karne lagey
  20,63,kehnay lagey yeh dono jadugar hain chahtay hain ke apne jaadoo ( ke zor ) se tum ko tumahray malik se nikal den aur tumahray shaista mazhab ko nabood kar dein
  20,64,to tum ( jaadoo ka ) samaan akatha karlo aur phir qitaar bandh kar aao. aaj jo ghalib raha wohi kamyaab howa
  20,65,bolay ke moose ya tum ( apni cheez ) daalo ya hum ( apni cheeze ) pehlay daaltay hain
  20,66,moose ne kaha nahi tum hi daalo. ( jab unhon ne cheeze dalain ) to nagahan un ki rasiyaan aur lathyan moose ke khayaal mein aisi anay lagen ke woh ( maidan ) mein idhar udhar daud rahi hain
  20,67,( uss waqt ) moose ne apne dil mein khauf maloomkiya
  20,68,hum ne kaha khauf nah karo bilashuba tum hi ghalib ho
  20,69,aur jo cheez ( yani laathi ) tumahray dahinay haath mein hai usay daal do ke jo kuch unhon ne banaya hai is ko nigal jaye gi. jo kuch unhon ne banaya hai ( yeh to ) gado garonke hthknde hain aur jadugar jahan jaye Falah nahi paye ga
  20,70,( al qissa yun hi howa ) to jadugar sjday mein gir parre ( aur ) kehnay lagey ke hum moose aur Haroon ke perwar-digaar par imaan laaye
  20,71,( firaon ) bola ke peshtar is ke mein tumhe ijazat dun tum is par imaan le aeye. be shak woh tumhara bara ( yani ustaad ) hai jis ne tum ko jaadoo sikhaya hai. so mein tumahray haath aur paon ( janib ) khilaaf se ktwa dun ga aur khajoor ke tnon par suli chrhhwa dun ga ( is waqt ) tum ko maloom hoga ke hum mein se kis ka azaab ziyada sakht aur der taq rehne wala hai
  20,72,unhon ne kaha jo dalail hamaray paas aagaye hain un par aur jis ne hum ko peda hai is par hum aap ko hargiz tarjeeh nahi den ge to aap ko jo hukum dena ho day dijiye. aur aap ( jo ) hukum day satke hain woh sirf isi duniya ki zindagi mein ( day satke hain )
  20,73,hum apne perwar-digaar par imaan le aeye taakay woh hamaray gunaaho ko maaf kere aur ( usay bhi ) jo aap ne hum se zabardasti jaadoo karaya. aur khuda behtar aur baqi rehne wala hai
  20,74,jo shakhs apne perwar-digaar ke paas gunehgaar ho kar aeye ga to is ke liye jahannum hai. jis mein nah marey ga nah jiye ga
  20,75,aur jo is ke rubaroo imandaar ho kar aeye ga aur amal bhi naik kiye hon ge to aisay logon ke liye ounchay ounchay darjay hain
  20,76,( yani ) hamesha rehne ke baagh jin ke neechay nehrain beh rahi hain. hamesha un mein rahen ge. aur yeh is shakhs ka badla hai jo pak howa
  20,77,aur hum ne moose ki taraf wahi bhaije ke hamaray bundon ko raton raat nikaal le jao phir un ke liye darya mein ( laathi maar kar ) khushk rasta bana do phir tum ko nah to ( firaon ke ) aa pakranay ka khauf hoga aur nah ( ghark honay ka ) dar
  20,78,phir firaon ne apne lashkar ke sath un ka taqubkiya to darya ( ki moajoon ) ne un par charh kar inhen dhaank liya ( yani duubo diya )
  20,79,aur firaon ne apni qoum ko gumraah kardiya aur seedhay raste par nah dala
  20,80,ae all Yaqoob hum ne tum ko tumahray dushman se nijaat di aur torat dainay ke liye tum se koh tor ki dahni taraf muqarrar ki aur tum par mann aur salwa nazilkiya
  20,81,( aur hukum diya ke ) jo pakeeza cheeze hum ne tum ko di hain un ko khao. aur is mein hadd se nah niklana. warna tum par mera ghazab nazil hoga. aur jis par mera ghazab nazil howa woh halaak hogaya
  20,82,aur jo tauba kere aur imaan laaye aur amal naik kere phir seedhay raste chalay is ko mein bakhash dainay wala hon
  20,83,aur ae moose tum ne apni qoum se ( agay chalay anay mein ) kyun jaldi ki
  20,84,kaha woh mere peechay ( aa rahay ) hain aur ae perwar-digaar mein ne teri taraf ( anay ki ) jaldi is liye ki ke to khush ho
  20,85,farmaya ke hum ne tumhari qoum ko tumahray baad azmaish mein daal diya hai aur samri ne un ko b_hka diya hai
  20,86,aur moose ghsse aur gham ki haalat mein apni qoum ke paas wapas aeye ( aur ) kehnay lagey ke ae qoumkiya tumahray perwar-digaar ne tum se aik acha wada nahikiya tha?kiya ( meri judai ki ) muddat tumhe daraaz ( maloom ) hui ya tum ne chaha ke tum par tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se ghazab nazil ho. aur ( is liye ) tum ne mujh se jo wadakiya tha ( is ke ) khilaafkiya
  20,87,woh kehnay lagey ke hum ne apne ikhtiyar se tum se wada khilaaf nahikiya. balkay hum logon ke زیوروں ka boojh uthaye hue they. phir hum ne is ko ( aag mein ) daal diya aur isi terhan samri ne daal diya
  20,88,to is ne un ke liye aik bitchrha bana diya ( yani is ka ) Qalib jis ki aawaz gaaye ki si thi. to log kehnay lagey ke yahi tumhara mabood hai aur moose ka bhi mabood hai. magar woh bhool gay hain
  20,89,kiya yeh log nahi dekhte ke woh un ki kisi baat ka jawab nahi deta. aur nah un ke nuqsaan aur naffa ka kuch ikhtiyar rakhta hai
  20,90,aur Haroon ne un se pehlay hi keh diya tha ke logo is se sirf tumhari azmaish ki gayi hai. aur tumhara perwar-digaar to khuda hai to meri pairwi karo aur mera kaha manu
  20,91,woh kehnay lagey ke jab taq moose hamaray paas wapas nah ayen hum to is ki pooja par qaim rahen ge
  20,92,( phir moose ne Haroon se ) kaha ke Haroon jab tum ne un ko dekha tha ke gumraah ho rahay hain to tum ko kis cheez ne roka
  20,93,( yani ) is baat se ke tum mere peechay chalay aao. bhala tum ne mere hukum ke khilaaf ( kyun )kiya ?
  20,94,kehnay lagey ke bhai meri darhhi aur sir ( ke balon ) ko nah pakriyay. mein to is se dara ke aap yeh nah kahin ke tum ne bani Israel mein tafarruqa daal diya aur meri baat ko malhooz nah rakha
  20,95,phir ( samri se ) kehnay lagey ke samri terakiya haal hai ?
  20,96,is ne kaha ke mein ne aisi cheez dekhi jo ouron ne nahi dekhi to mein ne farishtay ke naqsh pa se ( matti ki ) aik muthi bhar li. phir is ko ( bichhre ke Qalib mein ) daal diya aur mujhe mere jee ne ( is kaam ko ) acha bataya
  20,97,( moose ne ) kaha ja tujh ko duniya ki zindagi mein yeh ( saza ) hai ke kehta rahay ke mujh ko haath nah lagana aur tairay liye aik aur wada hai ( yani azaab ka ) jo tujh se tal nah sakay ga aur jis mabood ( ki pooja ) par to ( qaim o ) mutakif tha is ko dekh. hum usay jaladein ge phir is ( ki raakh ) ko urra kar darya mein bekhair den ge
  20,98,tumhara mabood khuda hi hai jis ke siwa koi mabood nahi. is ka ilm har cheez par muheet hai
  20,99,is terhan par hum tum se woh halaat bayan karte hain jo guzar chuke hain. aur hum ne tumhe apne paas se nasiyaat ( ki kitaab ) ataa farmai hai
  20,100,jo shakhs is se munh phairay ga woh qayamat ke din ( gunah ka ) boojh uthaiye ga
  20,101,( aisay log ) hamesha is ( azaab ) mein ( mubtala ) rahen ge aur yeh boojh qayamat ke roz un ke liye bura hai
  20,102,jis roz sor phonka jaye ga aur hum gunahgaaron ko akatha karen ge aur un ki ankhen niilii niilii hon gi
  20,103,( to ) woh aapas mein aahista aahista kahin ge ke tum ( duniya mein ) sirf das hi din rahay ho
  20,104,jo baatein yeh karen ge hum khoob jantay hain. is waqt un mein sab se achi raah wala ( yani Aqil وہوشمند ) kahe ga ke ( nahi balkay ) sirf aik hi roz thehray ho
  20,105,aur tum se pahoron ke baray mein daryaft karte hain. keh do ke khuda un ko urra kar bekhair day ga
  20,106,aur zameen ko hamwar maidan kar chhorey ga
  20,107,jis mein nah tum kajji ( aur pasti ) dekho ge nah teela ( aur bulandi )
  20,108,is roz log aik pukarnay walay ke peechay chalein ge aur is ki pairwi se inhiraf nah kar saken ge aur khuda ke samnay aawazian pust ho jaien gi to tum aawaz khfi ke siwa koi aawaz nah suno ge
  20,109,is roz ( kisi ki ) sifarish kuch faida nah day gi magar is shakhs ki jisay khuda ijazat day aur is ki baat ko pasand farmaiye
  20,110,jo kuch un ke agay hai aur kuch un ke peechay hai woh is ko jaanta hai aur woh ( apne ) ilm se khuda ( ke ilm ) par ihata nahi kar saktay
  20,111,aur is zindah o qaim ke ro baroo munh neechay ho jaien ge. aur jis ne zulm ka boojh uthaya woh namuraad raha
  20,112,aur jo naik kaam kere ga aur momin bhi hoga to is ko nah zulm ka khauf hoga aur nah nuqsaan ka
  20,113,aur hum ne is ko isi terhan ka quran arabi nazilkiya hai aur is mein terhan terhan ke draway bayan kardiye hain taakay log parhaizgaar banin ya khuda un ke liye nasiyaat peda kardey
  20,114,to khuda jo sacha badshah hai aliiiii qader hai. aur quran ki wahi jo tumhari taraf bhaije jati hai is ke poora honay se pehlay quran ke ( parhnay ke ) liye jaldi nahkiya karo aur dua karo ke mere perwar-digaar mujhe aur ziyada ilm day
  20,115,aur hum ne pehlay aadam se ehad liya tha magar woh ( usay ) bhool gay aur hum ne un mein sabr وثبات nah dekha
  20,116,aur jab hum ne firshton se kaha ke aadam ke agay sajda karo to sab sjday mein gir parre magar iblees ne inkaarkiya
  20,117,hum ne farmaya ke aadam yeh tumhara aur tumhari biwi ka dushman hai to yeh kahin tum dono ko bahisht se nikalwa nah day. phir tum takleef meinparr jao
  20,118,yahan tum ko yeh ( asayish ) hogi ke nah bhukay raho nah nangay
  20,119,aur yeh ke nah pyase raho aur nah dhoop khao
  20,120,to shetan ne un ke dil mein waswasa dala. ( aur ) kaha ke aadam bhala mein tum ko ( aisa ) darakht batau ( jo ) hamesha ki zindagi ka ( Samrah day ) aur ( aisi ) badshahat ke kabhi zael nah ho
  20,121,to dono ne is darakht ka phal kha liya to un par un ki sharmgahain zahir hogyin aur woh apne ( badnon ) par bahisht ke pattey chipkanay lagey. aur aadam ne apne perwar-digaar ke hukum ke khilaaf kiya to ( woh apne matloob se ) bay-raah ho gay-ay
  20,122,phir un ke perwar-digaar ne un ko nawaza to un par meharbani se tavajja farmai aur seedhi raah batayi
  20,123,farmaya ke tum dono yahan se neechay utar jao. tum mein baaz baaz ke dushman ( hon ge ) phir agar meri taraf se tumahray paas hadaayat aeye to jo shakhs meri hadaayat ki pairwi kere ga woh nah gumraah hoga aur nah takleef mein parre ga
  20,124,aur jo meri nasiyaat se munh phairay ga is ki zindagi tang hojaye gi aur qayamat ko hum usay andha karkay utthayen ge
  20,125,woh kahe ga mere perwar-digaar to ne mujhe andha karkay kyun uthaya mein to daikhta bhalta tha
  20,126,khuda farmaiye ga ke aisa hi ( chahiye tha ) tairay paas meri ayatain ayen to tunay un ko bhala diya. isi terhan aaj hum tujh ko bhala den ge
  20,127,aur jo shakhs hadd se nikal jaye aur apne perwar-digaar ki aayton par imaan nah laaye hum is ko aisa hi badla dete hain. aur akhirat ka azaab bohat sakht aur bohat der rehne wala hai
  20,128,kiya yeh baat un logon ke liye mojab hadaayat nah hui ke hum un se pehlay bohat se logon ko halaak kar chukay hain jin ke rehne ke maqamat mein yeh chaltay phirtay hain. aqal walon ke liye is mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
  20,129,aur agar aik baat tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se pehlay sadir aur ( jzaye aamaal ke liye ) aik meyaad muqarrar nah hochuki hoti to ( nuzool ) azaab lazim hojata
  20,130,pas jo kuch yeh bakwaas karte hain is par sabr karo. aur Sooraj ke niklny se pehlay aur is ke ghuroob honay se pehlay apne perwar-digaar ki tasbeeh tahmeed kiya karo. aur raat ki saa-at ( awaleen ) mein bhi is ki tasbeehkiya karo aur din ki atraaf ( yani dopehar ke qareeb Zahar ke waqt bhi ) taakay tum khush hojao
  20,131,aur kayi terhan ke logon ko jo hum ne duniya ki zindagi mein Araish ki cheezon se behra mandkiya hai taakay un ki azmaish karen un par nigah nah karna. aur tumhari perwar-digaar ki ( ataa farmai hui ) rozi bohat behtar aur baqi rehne wali hai
  20,132,aur apne ghar walon ko namaz ka hukum karo aur is par qaim raho. hum tum se rozi ke khawastgah nahi. balkay tumhe hum rozi dete hain aur ( naik ) injaam ( ahal ) taqwa ka hai
  20,133,aur kehte hain ke yeh ( paighambar ) apne perwar-digaar ki taraf se hamaray paas koi nishani kyun nahi laatay.kiya un ke paas pehli kitabon ki nishani nahi aayi ?
  20,134,aur agar hum un ko paighambar ( ke bhejnay ) se peshtar kisi azaab se halaak kardete to woh kehte ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar to ne hamari taraf koi paighambar kyun nah bheja ke hum zaleel aur ruswa honay se pehlay tairay kalaam (o ahkaam ) ki pairwi karte
  20,135,keh do ke sab ( nataij aamaal ) ke munhtazir hain so tum bhi munhtazir raho. anqareeb tum ko maloom hojaye ga ke ( deen ke ) seedhay raste par chalne walay kon hain aur ( jannat ki taraf ) raah panay walay kon hain ( hum ya tum )
